title: Looking for a Rookie ranked 5 team
body:
Hey guys, I am looking for a rookie ranked 5 team to begin playing more seriously with. I am a jungle main but can also play top and mid moderately well (just don't put me bot!). I would prefer not to have a toxic team. Can play a few games majority of evenings Brisbane time.

I am Silver 3 hoping to be Gold soon. Ideally the team would be like-minded people who want to improve their mechanics. 

Contact me please!

replies.body:
Hey,

I was looking to form/find a team as well. I'll give you a link to my thread, let me know if you're interested!!

Cheers,

Geoff
